  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      To investigate the efficacy and safety of three different doses of ASP2151, as compared to
      valacyclovir hydrochloride in subjects with herpes zoster, and to determine the recommended
      clinical dose.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
